snippet: Patrick Chan won his third title at the World Figure Skating Championships in London, Ontario, but the little-known Denis Ten of Kazakhstan stole the spotlight with a win in the free skate.
abstract: Patrick Chan wins his third title at the World Figure Skating Championship in London, Ontario.
lead_paragraph: Patrick Chan won his third title at the World Figure Skating Championships in London, Ontario, but the little-known Denis Ten of Kazakhstan stole the spotlight with a win in the free skate.
